---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Architecture | NetOps OS">
  <Header />
  <main class="page">
    <p class="label">Architecture</p>
    <h1>System Architecture</h1>
    <p class="lead">
      NetOps OS is planned as a modular, vendor-neutral system that can evolve from a simple control center into a full operations ecosystem.
    </p>

    <div class="card-grid">
      <article class="card"><h3>Frontend</h3><p>Modern web interface for engineers, operators, students, and NOC teams.</p></article>
      <article class="card"><h3>Backend API</h3><p>Core services for inventory, discovery, configuration, automation, and reports.</p></article>
      <article class="card"><h3>Database</h3><p>Structured storage for devices, sites, links, configurations, users, and reports.</p></article>
      <article class="card"><h3>Plugin Layer</h3><p>Future integrations for Cisco, Fortinet, MikroTik, Huawei, Linux, and other systems.</p></article>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</MainLayout>
